data.description: ***Huge Price Reduction*** Seller is motivated to sell! Pristine Santa Fe style home with Southwest design appeal and no HOA! Home features an open great room floor plan with 20 inch tile in main living and kitchen areas, slab granite counters, stainless steel appliances, glass cook top, and neutral two tone paint. The master bedroom has a bathroom with a nice sized, walk in shower and separate bath tub with large walk in closet. For those loving the outdoor living, your wait is over! Just in time for summer, this home features a covered patio with extended paver seating area and a sparkling pool perfect for the warm, summer days. Once winter hits, don't worry, this backyard has you covered with a gas outdoor fireplace and some of the most beautiful sunsets Arizona has to offer! Home is priced well below comps and is being sold in As-Is condition.
